import React from 'react';
import { Card, Button, Accordion } from 'react-bootstrap'



export default () => {
  return (
    <Accordion>
      <Card>
        <Card.Header>
          <Accordion.Toggle as={Button} variant="link" eventKey="0">
            Add a sandwich
          </Accordion.Toggle>
        </Card.Header>
        <Accordion.Collapse eventKey="0">
          <Card.Body>Hello! I'm the body</Card.Body>
        </Accordion.Collapse>
      </Card>
    </Accordion>
  )
}
